{"tid":1202680,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唯唯 - 梁競徽，三觀超正的愛港boy，這麼耿直你被圈粉了嗎？","createTime":"2019-06-11T10:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T10:27:48.000Z","uid":109923,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"faac26b8cb77cda1f23843861e4f21497d77b4fd","tid":1202680,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:03:48.000Z","msg":"為什麼說梁競徽三觀正並且愛港呢，因為梁競徽雖然去了中國發展，但是他仍然為自己是香港人而感到自豪，在參加69反送中遊行時，有人問他是中國香港人嗎，梁競徽立馬回答他是香港仔。<br />\n<br />\n長年在中國賺錢，內心卻不忘家鄉，大膽犀利的愛港心，可愛耿直的作風廣受香港人民好評以及愛戴，回港後又收穫了一大批的迷妹。<br />\n<br />\n在此我呼籲廣大的香港網民好好保護愛港boy，嚴打網絡發佈、散布唯唯遊行照片的行為，請大家低調在微信告訴大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fead345e276fd4aa97db82a76b0083b270d2b97b","tid":1202680,"uid":3860,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"呸 吃里扒外 口讲爱国 重要时候出卖党 以后别想赚咱们的钱"},{"pid":"b580917998f23facc3acf3115b68f5019f45bcbb","tid":1202680,"uid":3602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:11:11.000Z","msg":"圈粉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼￼勁fight￼￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923afe1f30c3361a654f206e2e63ab5231953bf0","tid":1202680,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯唯徽徽"},{"pid":"044044ed6faf8a92ad96a046b6648f9025d75691","tid":1202680,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T10:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}